data.meta_description: Clubs List | The Villages, FL - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document is a 107 page company listing report sorted alphabetically by company name. It includes the company name, full address, contact phone numbers, and company type, which is listed as "Resident Lifestyle Group" for most. The summary provides an overview but does not include any specific company details from the lengthy report.
